oji\" />"},{"pid":"8184dff7bb7f91f60316a9eb673fb29b5c354b61","tid":188902,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:13:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實幾好住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一出門口就有得同其他人玩，又可以養狗<br />\n係驚打風同火警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多昆蟲架"},{"pid":"65ce3ff8688a465d02f6fb64f059b36b142cc186","tid":188902,"uid":15205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:15:16.000Z","msg":"果個年代人與人之間既關係都幾好 , 唔會好似而家咁冷漠 , 成班細路仔一齊去公園球場玩"},{"pid":"e75ea6b87fb679b1dd7e02375ba7b15e302cd3ba","tid":188902,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:15:52.000Z","msg":"廢柴唔捱得嗰批都俾你吹奏到咁勁<br />\n以前通山走，四海為家，邊有鐵皮屋木屋住呀<br />\n食樹皮樹根，飲溪水，擔泥賺幾個豆令咪又係咁過<br />\n有鐵皮屋住已經好幸福架喇"},{"pid":"e9b85bf92b16fcf278cd9f241f051f5465f107bd","tid":188902,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:16:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>薄扶林村仲有冇人住</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有人住，但望落啲屋靚咗好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小學嗰時有兩個同學都係住薄扶林村<br />\n入到去成個迷宮咁<br />\n有時會幫手拎水去佢屋企"},{"pid":"2e32c21e4052f1a7b89f233f33b5860904d0eb4d","tid":188902,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:16:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53e3123afcfba24a858bcb64894ada2e7044c68f","tid":188902,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:37:28.000Z","msg":"你唔問埋無電腦點生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當你由細到大都無接觸過冷氣<br />\n你係唔會知冷氣既好處<br />\n<br />\n相反，接觸過冷氣，電話既老屎忽，你叫佢回歸返無冷氣無電話既生活，就會困難好多"},{"pid":"590525114dcf0a0c5b29e280bd38152b04b37c84","tid":188902,"uid":10460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:39:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>薄扶林村仲有冇人住</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有人住，但望落啲屋靚咗好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小學嗰時有兩個同學都係住薄扶林村<br />\n入到去成個迷宮咁<br />\n有時會幫手拎水去佢屋企</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小弟住緊薄扶林村<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1d90b76d1b539af2d21916501748a1f227fda4","tid":188902,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:39:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實幾好住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一出門口就有得同其他人玩，又可以養狗<br />\n係驚打風同火警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多昆蟲架</blockquote><br />\n成日捉黎玩架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a7acc64f826614f5e44109812c56ed715c0766","tid":188902,"uid":218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:41:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>薄扶林村仲有冇人住</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有人住，但望落啲屋靚咗好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小學嗰時有兩個同學都係住薄扶林村<br />\n入到去成個迷宮咁<br />\n有時會幫手拎水去佢屋企</blockquote><br />\n識兩家人都有自來水嘅"},{"pid":"fa2b80753894bac9515c7aba6c274e78aad416db","tid":188902,"uid":18465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T07:32:10.000Z","msg":"新界好多山頭都仲有大把人住緊呢d屋，都搭晒水電啦，自成一角成條村咁但係地圖係睇唔到有村名，入到去都唔知叫咩村"},{"pid":"5c072894c506f25ab62986c2e555f4f189d2a38e","tid":188902,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T07:37:08.000Z","msg":"以前香港天氣無咁差"},{"pid":"6fb8412354246aadbade7ef1cd312ee07a39bf3b","tid":188902,"uid":31368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T09:09:11.000Z","msg":"會唔會好多小強"},{"pid":"eafb67dec1cedadce